this standard. Please address the information to the IETF at
ietf-ipr@ietf.org.
WE checked the referenced BCP 78 but there is no information how the IETF documents are licensed to third parties. We then contacted the IETF we were told that the license of IETF documents for 3rd parties is described in the Trust-Legal-Provision, basically section 3, since the document was published in 2005 we took release 1.0 of the Legal-Trust-Provision. More we could not find dan the IETT was not able to provide more information.
Thus we concluded egal-Trust-Provision-1.0 as license of this file </text>
